<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>HUNE B2B Preview (Modo B)</title>
  <style>
    body{font-family:Arial;margin:0;background:#0b0f14;color:#e6e6e6}
    .wrap{max-width:860px;margin:60px auto;padding:0 20px}
    .card{background:#121a23;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:16px;padding:20px}
    input{width:100%;padding:12px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);background:#0b0f14;color:#e6e6e6;margin-top:8px}
    button{margin-top:14px;width:100%;padding:14px;border:0;border-radius:12px;background:#009bb5;color:#fff;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer}
    .err{margin-top:12px;background:rgba(255,82,82,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,82,82,.35);padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px}
    .hint{opacity:.75;font-size:12px;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.4}
    label{font-weight:800}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px;">HUNE B2B Preview (Modo B)</h1>
      <p style="opacity:.85;margin:0 0 14px;">Pegá una PDP del cliente + una PDP de Hune. Generamos preview en el layout del cliente + screenshot.</p>

      <form method="POST" action="/generate">
        <label>URL PDP Cliente (ejemplo)</label>
        <input name="clientUrl" placeholder="https://cliente.com/products/..." required />

        <label style="display:block;margin-top:14px;">URL PDP Hune</label>
        <input name="huneUrl" placeholder="https://www.hune.eco/products/haba-tws-sport" required />

        <button type="submit">Generar preview</button>
      </form>

      <% if (error) { %><div class="err"><b>Error:</b> <%= error %></div><% } %>

      <div class="hint">
        Nota: algunas webs bloquean bots o tienen estructuras raras. En esos casos, el próximo paso es permitir “selectores override” por sitio.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
